comment: Green (ORL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Oladipo (OKC) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Fournier (ORL) hops consecutively on the same foot upon retrieving the basketball.
[Observable in enhanced video] Fournier (ORL) moves his pivot foot.
Roberson (OKC) makes contact with Fournier's (ORL) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Ibaka (ORL) makes contact with Westbrook's (OKC) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court was upheld.
Vucevic (ORL) sets the screen on Roberson (OKC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Ibaka (ORL) and Kanter (OKC) make incidental contact in their attempt to retrieve the rebound.
Fournier (ORL) and Westbrook (OKC) briefly engage and separate on the perimeter.
